          <p>HON. FRANK CORBETT : Madam Speaker, on behalf of the Premier, I hereby give notice that on a future day I shall move the following resolution:</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MADAM SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MADAM SPEAKER : Order, please. We're not quite there yet. This is Statements by Ministers and I've had a request for an introduction. Sorry to interrupt you.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#6fd8b406-a075-4718-b5e3-c33555ca4243">
          <from>MR. KEITH BAIN</from>
          <p>MR. KEITH BAIN : Thank you, Madam Speaker. I'm pleased to make an introduction of two individuals who are in the Speaker's Gallery this afternoon. I would ask that Mike Skinner and Dave McKillop please rise.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
